<p>Every element must be part of a <span>fieldset</span>, otherwise the styles won't be rendered appropriately (accessiblity considerations aside).</p>
<pre>
	<code>
&lt;form&gt;<br/>  &lt;fieldset&gt;<br/>    &lt;p&gt;<br/>      &lt;label&gt;This is the label&lt;/label&gt;<br/>      &lt;input type=&quot;text&quot; value=&quot;Some predefined text here&quot;&gt;<br/>    &lt;/p&gt;<br/>  &lt;/fieldset&gt;<br/>&lt;/form&gt;
	</code>
</pre>

